{"tid":1061325,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【港滙偏弱】澳新銀行楊宇霆：今年未必大規模走資","createTime":"2019-03-14T10:23:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-14T12:49:03.000Z","uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"26988d269068934bbc5c5b0eccfc674071a68bb1","tid":1061325,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T10:23:38.000Z","msg":"港滙近期徘徊在弱方兌換保證水平，金管局上周六清晨承接約15億港元沽盤，是近半年以來首次接錢。澳新銀行大中華區首席經濟學家楊宇霆預計，今年未必發生大規模走資，預期港滙會在7.85水平徘徊，即使觸及弱方保證亦不足為懼。<br />\n<br />\n他又預期，美國將於今年加息一次，最快會在6月發生，估計聯儲局將於年內停止縮表，但不認同聯儲局會突然減息。在美息上升空間有限的大前提下，他認為香港利率難會抽升，包括樓市等資產價格會受惠。<br />\n<br />\n對於美元近期在97水平整固，楊宇霆表示，主要是歐央行放水，導致歐元走弱，對美元構成支持，一旦美國加息，美元將進一步回升，料人民幣年底目標見每美元兌6.75元人民幣。他又補充，內地刺激經濟政策具體，加上流動性充裕，相信可支持內地股市溫和上升。<br />\n<br />\n記者：黃珮琳<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190312/59360412\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190312%2F59360412&d=%2FIrJ3RR%2Fwz8SFLZOEAJhpr4BfDbUEiSkD5bB26vbFoA%3D&h=e749c94d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190312%2F59360412&h=6fe8b8de\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190312/59360412</a>"},{"pid":"f6f2e88a08cf96be03f830d568009eb006e5bd19","tid":1061325,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T10:30:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e331e52923a8a5e6fb6ad06c102bdbd9c129b51","tid":1061325,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T12:08:42.000Z","msg":"掂一掂就瓜瓜嘈<br />\n敏感過你老母g點"},{"pid":"3af6f9a1a8e0553041b13d502bb5be74d29025ad","tid":1061325,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T12:49:0